V'aThH Sh'a QYNH 'aL-NShY'aY YShUr'aL.
V'aMUrTh MH 'aMK LBY'a BYN 'aUrYVTh UrBTShH BThVK KPhUrYM UrBThH GVUrYH.
VTh'yL 'aChD MGUrYH KPhYUr HYH VYLMD LTUrPh-TUrPh 'aDM 'aKL.
VYShM'yV 'aLYV GVYM BShChThM NThPhSh VYB'aHV BChChYM 'aL-'aUrTSh MTShUrYM.
VThUr'a KY NVChLH 'aBDH ThQVThH VThQCh 'aChD MGUrYH KPhYUr ShMThHV.
VYThHLK BThVK-'aUrYVTh KPhYUr HYH VYLMD LTUrPh-TUrPh 'aDM 'aKL.
VYD'y 'aLMNVThYV V'yUrYHM HChUrYB VThShM 'aUrTSh VML'aH MQVL Sh'aGThV.
VYThNV 'yLYV GVYM SBYB MMDYNVTh VYPhUrShV 'yLYV UrShThM BShChThM NThPhSh.
VYThNHV BSVGUr BChChYM VYB'aHV 'aL-MLK BBL YB'aHV BMTShDVTh LM'yN L'a- YShM'y QVLV 'yVD 'aL-HUrY YShUr'aL.
'aMK KGPhN BDMK 'yL-MYM ShThVLH PhUrYH V'yNPhH HYThH MMYM UrBYM.
VYHYV-LH MTVTh 'yZ 'aL-ShBTY MShLYM VThGBH QVMThV 'yL-BYN 'yBThYM VYUr'a BGBHV BUrB DLYThYV.
VThThSh BChMH L'aUrTSh HShLKH VUrVCh HQDYM HVBYSh PhUrYH HThPhUrQV VYBShV MTH 'yZH 'aSh 'aKLThHV.
V'yThH ShThVLH BMDBUr B'aUrTSh TShYH VTShM'a.
VThTSh'a 'aSh MMTH BDYH PhUrYH 'aKLH VL'a-HYH BH MTH-'yZ ShBT LMShVL QYNH HY'a VThHY LQYNH.
